</ul>
</nav>

</header>

<div class="prescription">

<h1>TeleMedicine Hospital</h1>
<h2>Digital Prescription</h2>

<div class="info">
<p><strong>Patient Name:</strong> Ravi Kumar</p>
<p><strong>Age:</strong> 30</p>
<p><strong>Doctor:</strong> Dr. Kumar</p>
<p><strong>Date:</strong> 05-07-2026</p>
<p><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> Viral Fever</p>
</div>

<table>

<tr>
<th>Medicine</th>
<th>Dosage</th>
<th>Duration</th>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Paracetamol 500mg</td>
<td>1 Tablet - 3 Times/Day</td>
<td>5 Days</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Vitamin C</td>
<td>1 Tablet - Daily</td>
<td>7 Days</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Cough Syrup</td>
<td>10 ml - Twice/Day</td>
<td>5 Days</td>
</tr>

</table>

<div class="buttons">

<button class="download" onclick="downloadPrescription()">
Download Prescription
</button>

<button class="print" onclick="window.print()">
Print Prescription
</button>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 TeleMedicine Access for Rural Healthcare</p>

</footer>

